r_debut.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/holostars_english_new_unit_armis_4_vtuber_debut.jpg?fit=1200%2C675&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/holostars_english_new_unit_armis_4_vtuber_debut.jpg?resize=1100%2C619&#038;ssl=1" alt="Holostars English 新组合“ARMIS”的 4 位新 VTuber 首次亮相" class="wp-image-106446" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p>这次登场的艺人是“ <strong>Jurard T</strong> Rexford”、“ <strong>Goldbullet</strong> ”、“ <strong>Octavio</strong> ”、“ <strong>Crimzon Ruze</strong> ”。这就是名字。</p><p></p><h2 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading"> Holostars 英语-ARMIS- </h2><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【#holoARMIS】- ARMIS- HOLOSTARS EN【出道PV】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gDBKJzo69E0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHdaBFLRvHq4Teq9zPtrQL8lxb-l3jZL3vU2ZkIHCjdvOEO-VaVNUdNeYVVh8LOYYv-13HVUTFuu3k-uqEWndVTWfOreXJpUo6xOnlyXJGlmfvJ11At3QprZaCvSfIOuHTE0D9m0K6OparDuJWBsc3aC=w1097-h412-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p> ARMIS是对抗TEMPUS六名成员的“最强赏金猎人”组织。</p><p>他以消灭腐烂的野兽为生，目标是快速致富！开辟新未来！</p><p></p><h2 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">贾拉德·T·雷克斯福德</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHepLwgYrXt7j-zIcM3SU5eNhuB9og7CcLA8ZNM-AjA4y09QsEiDGqzswMlewefcbvyMzeTDuQs1lWfiy2sSZq3zTbSsnEPqyzPcqzxQhD3ozIZ9ro9P55NETeYFi-MB5N9K21eVOtHrQ73NLU-ISYQD=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © 2016 COVER Corp.</figcaption></figure><p> <strong>“你们都输了！”</strong></p><p>我是拥有恐龙基因、座右铭是适者生存的最强王子。<br>当他兴奋或生气时，有时会表现出凶猛的一面。<br>征服野兽时使用两把手枪。<br>他认为金钱和权力就能解决一切，性格自私。<br>他最喜欢的词是“快速致富”和“巨额奖金”。<br>对我来说，目前的趋势是国际象棋，但我不知道它会持续多久，因为它太善变了。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【#holoARMIS】- Jurard T Rexford - HOLOSTARS EN【首次亮相PV】" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/cEGSJBZSwpM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>哈班 (@haban35)</td></tr><tr><td>实时二维设计</td><td>Ammachi Gogogo (@takamachigo3)</td></tr><tr><td> YouTube 官方频道</td><td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/@JurardTRexford" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="Jurard T Rexford Ch. HOLOSTARS-EN">Jurard T Rexford Ch. HOLOSTARS-EN</a></td></tr><tr><td> X（推特）官方账号</td><td><a href="https://twitter.com/jurardtrexford" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="贾拉德·T·雷克斯福德🦖HOLOSTARS CN">贾拉德·T·雷克斯福德<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f996.png" alt="🦖" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />全息星 CN</a></td></tr><tr><td>预定首发发行日期</td><td>2023年（令和5年）11月18日（周六）12:00~<br> （日本时间）</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">首次发行网址： <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rr5n5dJMmPU" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">https://www.youtube.com/watch</a> ?v=rr5n5dJMmPU</figcaption></figure><p></p><h2 id="outline__3" class="wp-block-heading">金子弹</h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHeF0zWHsIy3rC-5y-z62Yqw4UCnrIj84KDjKC8N